{"tid":158213,"cid":12,"subCid":0,"title":"［喪屍］香港。我要在這座喪屍城生存下去 (2)","createTime":"2017-03-16T06:24:03.000Z","updateTime":"2019-03-09T23:07:29.000Z","uid":31552,"like":51,"dislike":17,"uniUserReply":1,"replies":[{"pid":"83e698299a0398390868bba0ce2e8e7157d285d2","tid":158213,"uid":31552,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-16T06:24:03.000Z","msg":"Post 1 :<a href=\"https://lihkg.com/thread/103317/page/1\" target=\"_blank\">https://lihkg.com/thread/103317/page/1</a><br />\n<br />\n故事既原創者係巴打「拾叄少」。<br />\n<br />\n唔知巴打出咩事，五日之前就突然失蹤，停曬故，見好多巴打都好唔捨得個故就咁停左。咁我之前就上載左一篇，見都有幾位巴打叫作落去，咁我就嘗試延續落去，小弟我都係第一次作故，有咩唔好請見諒同埋比下意見。<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8f45bbe0d4a30cbbea66e9957432007baa5e3a89","tid":158213,"uid":31552,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-16T06:24:45.000Z","msg":"第六十二節 ｰ 購物中心 (下)<br />\n<br />\n「砰！砰！砰！砰！砰！⋯⋯」<br />\n腳步聲愈來愈近，已經可以感受到喪屍的身形是何等巨大。因為每一下既腳步聲，都搭配住一下又一下既震盪。<br />\n<br />\n「宜加點算阿？佢好似愈黎愈近啦，再唔走就黎唔切啦！」<br />\n呂麗翹擺住一副好驚既樣問我。<br />\n<br />\n我心諗：「屌你老母臭閪，博一博單車都變摩托，等我沖出去引走條肥屍先，咪如果真係攬炒。」<br />\n<br />\n「你地陣間向我反方向走出去呢個商場，我會引走隻肥屍，我地係門口等。」我一臉認真咁望住佢地講。<br />\n<br />\n「好危險阿咁樣，你估你係保特咩，隻肥屍實追到你架！」<br />\n妹妹十分緊張咁講。<br />\n<br />\n「你係唔係想一齊死？」<br />\n我好認真咁望住阿妹講。<br />\n<br />\n阿軒同呂麗翹擺出左一副好信任我既眼神，但其實我知道呂麗翹心底係好擔心我，我埋去佢道錫左佢額頭一下，因為我唔知道我呢次出去仲有無命番黎。<br />\n<br />\n交代晒所有野之後，我就衝左出去。<br />\n<br />\n當我一衝左出去，係我眼前既喪屍，比起岩岩個隻肥佬喪屍更加大隻，係個隻肥佬喪屍既三倍。我心諗：「呢獲真係含家剷。」<br />\n<br />\n62完"},{"pid":"c89464f4ed7978b7acb24bc48e8c6d6387852420","tid":158213,"uid":31552,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-16T07:32:49.000Z","msg":"推一推<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6e22443519facc6aac9741043c92e918e7786193","tid":158213,"uid":31552,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-16T07:35:12.000Z","msg":"第六十三節 ｰ 千鈞一發<br />\n<br />\n「會唔會係咁大隻。。。」<br />\n眼前的是一隻約半層樓高的喪屍，它比起街市的肥喪還要大隻。<br />\n<br />\n「喂！過黎呢邊阿！死肥佬！」<br />\n我大聲叫囂著，希望吸引到它的注意，說罷，它已經把目光轉移到我身上。<br />\n<br />\n「呀！！！！」<br />\n喪屍像暴走一樣，發了瘋的追著我。<br />\n<br />\n「走阿你地！！！門口等啦！！！」<br />\n我拔足狂奔，試圖用最快的速度把它引到最遠的地方，但它也追得十分緊貼，就在我兩三個馬位之近，若它撲向我，必死無疑。<br />\n<br />\n此時我看到右方有一個走火通道，我立馬轉向右邊一直跑過去，希望能夠從那裡逃走，至少也能阻隔它一段時間，好令我有更多的時間把它扔開，回到商場門口與他們會合。<br />\n<br />\n「仆街！對門點會反鎖左架？」<br />\n我忍不住怒氣叫了出來，在沒人的商場，走火通道竟然反鎖了。<br />\n<br />\n此時，那隻巨形喪屍已經向我一步一步逼近，它的每一步也震懾著我的心，而我亦已無退路，緊緊的貼著走火通道的門口，像是等待死亡的來臨。<br />\n<br />\n我到處張望，在想有什麼東西好令我能夠逃脫，可是，一樣也沒有。<br />\n<br />\n此時巨形喪屍已經離我只有兩個馬位，只要它揮拳向我，便能把我擊斃。<br />\n<br />\n「呀！！！！！」<br />\n它向我大聲咆哮，像是向我渲洩一樣，告訴我必死無疑的那樣。<br />\n<br />\n我腦海中只有浮現與呂麗翹由地鐵相遇後的一切一切，有她在的每一刻，好像什麼也變得特別安心，總能令我的心情輕易平伏，保護她好像成了我生命中的一部分那樣。還記得她笑起上來甜甜的樣子，她生氣時的可愛樣子，什至是睡著的樣子，醉酒鬧事的樣子，也在我腦海中一一出現，現在發現自己原來已經愛上她。<br />\n<br />\n「太遲了吧。」<br />\n我緊閉雙眼，準備迎接死亡，原來死亡也不是那麼可怕。<br />\n<br />\n「哈哈哈哈！」<br />\n<br />\n「？！」"},{"pid":"b615aade5e4d107ef8cc42b7e1828429f597f0db","tid":158213,"uid":54387,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-16T07:42:11.000Z","msg":"支持，請繼續<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9e360340a942adf0d990493a4a6dec504c9037f2","tid":158213,"uid":53413,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-16T07:43:19.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5c9e5e6a943b61ff308a2171c8a5d26c3b00a5af","tid":158213,"uid":31552,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-16T09:46:31.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>支持，請繼續<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n多謝巴打支持<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a3921bee90cebd9e39cb9d3c59d9d5d3f3cbe4df","tid":158213,"uid":31552,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-16T09:47:26.000Z","msg":"如果今晚有十個正皮，再出多篇<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6f86480c1bd213da65b2bf60957c9711a9d2ef71","tid":158213,"uid":48483,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-16T09:58:08.000Z","msg":"皮已正<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n名已留<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8bef03bbd5478bbb36f5ca69a707e5c28d6c8191","tid":158213,"uid":67882,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-16T10:04:21.000Z","msg":"支持<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"05c83aff9f2ed951a36a60f3d5f7072f12e05892","tid":158213,"uid":31552,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-16T10:28:35.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>皮已正<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n名已留<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n多謝巴打<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3f21d6a81b8c5bac18b771821005b4fe3ecb30f1","tid":158213,"uid":31552,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-16T10:28:59.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>支持<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n多謝巴打<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1d2fee41b8b635e647cca98507a85c3f47f889f7","tid":158213,"uid":15237,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-16T10:51:58.000Z","msg":"原來唔同左人寫， style 好唔同"},{"pid":"689c3698f3632487f1b62002f21abc53b41413bc","tid":158213,"uid":66254,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-16T11:21:36.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1126a11b1e29fa362fb8b539dcda3c6cf407d671","tid":158213,"uid":31552,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-16T12:02:15.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>原來唔同左人寫， style 好唔同</blockquote><br />\n係阿，真係有點難食之前個位巴打既用語，抱歉，但我都會努力作好佢<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9e6b1665f099dc87b76ce8a5d4ec692b67be2db0","tid":158213,"uid":26300,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-16T15:51:43.000Z","msg":"正皮我俾嘅<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4b0f49e3cd6372835dec81ad3142af18b9a05031","tid":158213,"uid":3812,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-16T16:22:05.000Z","msg":"巴打好有心<br />\n加油<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ba65ef6530625a4d675817219c4a369a8b5e21f8","tid":158213,"uid":91240,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-16T16:34:14.000Z","msg":"皮已正<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"62add83d987602cd2436c7af299f19cbf2ddc504","tid":158213,"uid":61105,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-16T16:34:29.000Z","msg":"巴打加油，不過都希望原作者快d番黎<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e71d02b1cf70f67eb2d5a047a7ad75324db83f0a","tid":158213,"uid":31552,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-16T16:35:05.000Z","msg":"第六十四節 ｰ 安全離去<br />\n<br />\n「哈哈哈哈！你睇下個垃圾，宜加比隻喪屍屈左係死角，準備收皮啦！」<br />\n「哈！抵撚佢死啦，岩岩打到我地咁。」<br />\n原來是剛才給我打到半死的兩個男人，他們站在二樓的欄杆邊，看到我快要死去，興奮得忘形，但我也無話可說，剛才打成他們這樣，換著是我也會這樣興奮。<br />\n<br />\n「呀！！！」<br />\n巨形喪屍再次咆哮。心想這次真的必死無疑，我閉上眼睛，等待死亡的來臨。<br />\n<br />\n「阿妹、麗翹，對唔住，我諗我再保護唔到你地啦。」<br />\n我心想。<br />\n<br />\n此時我感覺到巨形喪屍反方向走開了，它的方向正正是向著剛才叫囂的兩個男人。 <br />\n巨形喪屍下一秒便向著他們狂奔，而它也隨手拿起了一個垃圾桶，拋了過去。<br />\n<br />\n「大獲！走阿喂！」<br />\n其中一個男人大叫，可是巨形喪屍已經十分快速的在他們腳下，它一手向上揮拳。<br />\n<br />\n天花馬上倒塌，那兩個男人亦與碎石一起掉下來。在那一剎那巨形喪屍抓住了給我打爆牙的那個男人，把他的身體上下分屍。<br />\n<br />\n「嗚啊！！！唔好殺我阿！！！！」<br />\n另一個男人叫著，可是他已被碎石壓住雙腳，無法動彈，情況相當可憐。<br />\n<br />\n在同一時間，巨形喪屍已把口上的美食放進口中，目光亦開始轉向躺在地上的男人。準備向他埋手，品嚐最後的美食，他一邊伸手過去，男人一邊瘋狂大叫，更不停掙扎著，希望能夠逃走，可是他根本沒法動彈。<br />\n<br />\n見狀我便馬上向原路逃走，不停狂奔，我不敢放慢腳步，生怕巨形喪屍再次追上的，假如再被它追多次，以我的體力一定應付不到。<br />\n<br />\n再次回到剛才的藏身點，我便向著左邊的出口走去，再跑大約50m，到電梯口，已見到阿軒等人向我招手。我馬上跑到他們身旁。<br />\n<br />\n「你無事就好啦，我地等左你好耐，以為你有咩事阿！本來我想去搵你架，但阿軒唔比。」呂麗翹攬著我說，還帶有一點淚水。<br />\n<br />\n「岩岩差d真係番唔到黎見你架啦，好彩個兩個男人出現，做左替死鬼。」<br />\n我安慰著麗翹說。<br />\n<br />\n「咩替死鬼？」<br />\n阿軒等人一起追問。<br />\n<br />\n「我地行住番去講啦。」<br />\n說罷我們便踏上回家的路途，同時我亦向他們複述剛才的驚險情況。<br />\n<br />\n「原來係咁。好彩你番到黎咋，咪如果得番我一個男人都唔知點算，你個妹同呂麗翹實喊到痴線。」<br />\n阿軒揶揄她們。<br />\n<br />\n「咩啊！！」<br />\n呂麗翹臉紅著說。<br />\n<br />\n「Sorry！我唔會有感覺囉！」<br />\n阿妹輕挑地說著。<br />\n<br />\n眾人都哈哈地大笑著。<br />\n<br />\n「啊！係喎，唔記得同你講，我岩岩係你跑左去反方向既時候，沖左上去二樓間鋪頭拎左好多包種子，陣間我地番去睇下有咩可以種黎食。」<br />\n阿軒向我說。<br />\n<br />\n「睇黎我地呢次出動無白費到！你係得既阿軒！」<br />\n「洗乜講？」<br />\n<br />\n64完"},{"pid":"9bda98dfb83e41a6411e3aaaa441b68a507f39d1","tid":158213,"uid":31552,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-16T16:37:06.000Z","msg":"多謝咁多位巴打既支持！<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n但我想同大家講番先，我都係一邊作一邊等緊拾叄少巴打出番文。<br />\n當佢出番文我就唔會再作落去架啦。<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/ass.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"86dbe4065d9977869c55c2ad9c31e395bb68a548","tid":158213,"uid":31040,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-16T16:52:18.000Z","msg":"皮已正"},{"pid":"46e07c7e95bb15466ef30fb06626b7951d5cf862","tid":158213,"uid":15481,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-16T19:34:59.000Z","msg":"唔理咁撚多<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n有文睇就得<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4526f8492a29f34c17e4893ae16e93219adf618f","tid":158213,"uid":73821,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-16T21:29:32.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"a1cc5d1a883f3a51abf136740fb8d493865c8378","tid":158213,"uid":34023,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-17T00:04:51.000Z","msg":"半層樓高。。好撚矮ja wo"},{"pid":"7887d31805ecad5b4f0f06f78197f0c4988f1243","tid":158213,"uid":31552,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-17T00:42:45.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>半層樓高。。好撚矮ja wo</blockquote><br />\n都夠一招收你皮<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b04b73846c1f45f814539eaead648e22dc2562a9","tid":158213,"uid":54387,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-17T01:32:38.000Z","msg":"好睇！"},{"pid":"faa93b015648cf31cf54f02cc353077207cf347b","tid":158213,"uid":85087,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-17T02:49:48.000Z","msg":"留個名先"},{"pid":"860a0a42a3f7a7cabf64626127f5e47bb32d7d49","tid":158213,"uid":27265,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-17T05:45:32.000Z","msg":"靠你啦巴打 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0a72fa6da8a180b31c06e5ac495acb8352635c7b","tid":158213,"uid":11971,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-17T06:51:33.000Z","msg":"咁多類型嘅故入面我最鍾意睇屍故<br />\n多謝巴打你延續呢個故<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"48d72b62c1767eea5f7232c00b7692e552ccb68c","tid":158213,"uid":75719,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-17T07:40:28.000Z","msg":"巴打加油<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />  我都等緊原作者作落去<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ffadfcdb786e82103d2f97d075e614cd7b5de616","tid":158213,"uid":31552,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-17T08:51:39.000Z","msg":"因為最近都比較忙，所以可能都會一日一篇先，如果有時間我會出多一篇<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/09.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n再一次多謝大家的支持<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/09.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/09.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d03fee1693dcd5a565d9dda9b6f9cbe1c0f72470","tid":158213,"uid":48483,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-17T09:15:46.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>因為最近都比較忙，所以可能都會一日一篇先，如果有時間我會出多一篇<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/09.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n再一次多謝大家的支持<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/09.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/09.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n加油<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f90d0e1063fb5ef0067e25b61b4abdf12af228dd","tid":158213,"uid":24049,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-17T13:58:30.000Z","msg":"唔好爛尾<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c419a628ceab721c02626252e88bfeeef1ee48bf","tid":158213,"uid":31552,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-17T15:27:14.000Z","msg":"第六十五節 &mdash; 重新計劃<br />\n「嗨！你地番黎啦？無出咩事阿嘛？小姐呢？小姐你有無事阿？無整親嘛？」<br />\n工人姐姐問道。<br />\n<br />\n「無事阿，有驚無險，安全番到黎！」<br />\n呂麗翹微笑的回應，示意工人姐姐不用擔心。<br />\n<br />\n「大家都休息下先，晚飯時間我有件事要同大家講。」<br />\n頓時感到各人都變得嚴肅起來。<br />\n<br />\n「無乜野既，都只不過係同大家講下我地宜加既處境，同埋未來既打算，我地都唔可以一直留係呢道，大家去休息下先，陣間再傾。」<br />\n說罷我也先回房間休息。<br />\n<br />\n雖然說今天發生的事不太多，但其實每個畫面也揮之不去，包括那一隻巨形喪屍，我以為在街市的那一隻已經很誇張，怎料還有一隻半層樓（約五米）高的巨形喪屍，假如再遇上多次，很可能我們都會全軍覆沒。<br />\n<br />\n更何況現在我們的隊伍，實在無法有太快速的行動，事關我們總共有五個女仔：呂麗翹、林小蕊、工人姐姐、阿妹、曈曈，這也是其中一個隱憂。我和阿軒根本無法照顧他們。<br />\n<br />\n嶺南大學與清水灣的距離亦相當遙遠，徒步過去亦是不可能。<br />\n<br />\n「！！」<br />\n突然想起呂麗翹的家中，有一部跑車，或許我能和阿軒再到外面尋找物資，並且先行探一探路，令我們能制定路線，以最快速的方法去到嶺南大學。<br />\n沒錯，我們的目標是嶺南大學。<br />\n<br />\n晚上8時正。<br />\n<br />\n「食飯啦食飯啦！快啲落黎啦！」<br />\n工人姐姐叫喊著，眾人開始聚集在飯廳中。<br />\n<br />\n「辛苦你啦！蓮姐！」<br />\n呂麗翹微笑地點頭。<br />\n<br />\n「哦？原來你叫蓮姐阿？點解咁耐以黎你都唔同我地講既？等我地仲成日叫你工人姐姐，HAHA」<br />\n阿妹說著。<br />\n<br />\n「無所謂啦，都係一句姐，大家食飯啦！」<br />\n蓮姐回答說。<br />\n<br />\n眾人都有笑有說，唯獨我一個人沈默不語，我亦沒有心情跟他們說閒話，因為我必須以他們的安全為首，必定要把他們安全送到總部，儘管最後什至要犧牲自己。<br />\n<br />\n呂麗翹也察覺到我沒發過一點聲，就揶揄我說。<br />\n「喂！你係咪岩岩比隻喪屍嚇到傻左阿？」<br />\n「唔係。諗緊野姐。」<br />\n「哦！咁好囉！快啲食野啦！」<br />\n<br />\n「哎喲！麗翹大過女啦hehe！」<br />\n小蕊看到這狀況便道出了這句話，使呂麗翹都通紅了。<br />\n<br />\n「咩啊！邊有！我叫佢食飯咋嘛。」<br />\n呂麗翹急忙解釋著。<br />\n<br />\n畫面又再次活在笑聲之中。<br />\n<br />\n晚飯過後，我示意大家到大廳一聚。<br />\n<br />\n我把剛才所想的都全告訴他們。<br />\n<br />\n「其實我地係呢道都唔可以留得太耐，之前我去搵阿妹既時候，識左一個叫宋慧珊既女仔，佢係一個部隊既隊長，我臨走既時候，佢比左總部既地標比我，而地點就係嶺南大學。大家都知道離呢道有幾十公里，過去並唔容易，所以我聽朝會同阿軒出去探探路，睇下有咩最快既路可以令我地比較安全咁過去，麗翹我想問你借部跑車。」<br />\n<br />\n「好阿！無問題，要小心啲阿！」<br />\n呂麗翹也沒再追問那麼多。<br />\n「好！」<br />\n「我要講既都講曬架啦，大家可以早啲休息。」<br />\n說罷那三個女生又一起去洗澡。<br />\n沖涼房的吵鬧聲又再次傳出來，浮現出在阿軒嫲嫲的美好回憶。<br />\n<br />\n「軒嫲嫲，對不起。」<br />\n<br />\n65完"},{"pid":"d7c2b0a712a206c4fc1ba32b094790f900a2f495","tid":158213,"uid":31552,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-17T15:28:30.000Z","msg":"由於聽日有野要做，可能出唔到文，所以今日出大篇小小，謝罪！<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"954059a239aaf9473ea1eeecd9a73c3a0bdfa7be","tid":158213,"uid":27265,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-17T15:37:43.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>由於聽日有野要做，可能出唔到文，所以今日出大篇小小，謝罪！<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n辛苦啦巴打！<br />\n慢慢！重質不重量<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0a86df645f08fb7bcc5ef1bc9074968e4cf8c8f0","tid":158213,"uid":3166,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-17T15:41:32.000Z","msg":"巴打真係有心<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 辛苦了<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 加油"},{"pid":"a426ebf232a15edbd60c4627639675a36f81c835","tid":158213,"uid":54387,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-17T23:01:47.000Z","msg":"我覺得好睇過原著"},{"pid":"7bc23a1f1b0e1941aba31738eaece97128cebeb2","tid":158213,"uid":52708,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-18T04:46:14.000Z","msg":"留名<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"fdd67e11e3cb50a48dcdb456b353a0b23155cc98","tid":158213,"uid":31552,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-18T06:47:25.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>我覺得好睇過原著</blockquote><br />\n竟然<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/surprise.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 多謝你先<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"959e129a031bfa8ff94e9fc6cb8aafd4ab4838eb","tid":158213,"uid":87404,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-18T09:02:41.000Z","msg":"巴打加油<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n表示後段麗翹可唔可以唔好死<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5a4c9fc4b78b2b6f64845b2a31900b5e6ed78b11","tid":158213,"uid":61709,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-18T14:40:40.000Z","msg":"打鬥可以試下寫多啲，加啲唔同種類既招式，直拳，左勾拳，則踢，打左腰打雞心，會細緻啲<br />\n<br />\n同埋可以試下加方向，比如同隊長合擊個陣 我從左方 佢右方咁"},{"pid":"db87452bcde600884999ce35f04a34c8b4ea29e7","tid":158213,"uid":31552,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-18T15:19:35.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>打鬥可以試下寫多啲，加啲唔同種類既招式，直拳，左勾拳，則踢，打左腰打雞心，會細緻啲<br />\n<br />\n同埋可以試下加方向，比如同隊長合擊個陣 我從左方 佢右方咁</blockquote><br />\n好既 多謝巴打指點<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"df7df3c8e0eac2551b6ffe78f5b0cb9d46aea5dd","tid":158213,"uid":31552,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-19T01:39:42.000Z","msg":"第六十六節 &mdash; 搜索<br />\n<br />\n第二天的早上，我洗了個澡，便去找阿軒出發。<br />\n<br />\n「你準備好未？」<br />\n隨手我便把跑車的鎖匙拋了給他。<br />\n<br />\n「死仔，晨早流流考我反應力阿？行啦！」<br />\n阿軒一手便把鎖匙接了下來，一面得戚的看著我。<br />\n<br />\n我也沒他那麼好氣，便反了他一下白眼。<br />\n<br />\n「我地宜加係小坑口，要行龍蝦灣路，再行清水灣道直出去坑口。始終個邊都比較多商場，同埋我諗我地都要入去將軍澳警署睇下有無物資岩用。」<br />\n我向阿軒解釋著。<br />\n<br />\n「無問題啦，點解你咁長氣架，比隻巨形喪屍嚇到你傻左？」<br />\n阿軒嘲笑我。<br />\n<br />\n「你試下如果係你？你嚇傻左啦！」<br />\n我鄙視他說。<br />\n<br />\n「講笑姐，出發啦！」<br />\n阿軒傻笑著說。<br />\n<br />\n「哇，我都未試過渣咁靚既跑車。」<br />\n他踏著油門，開至110km/h<br />\n<br />\n「你係咪痴線架，你係咪唔記得左自己P牌咋，頂你個肺，開慢d啦！！」<br />\n我從未試過這種速度，而且車很晃動得誇張，使我有點流額汗。<br />\n<br />\n「哎，牛高馬大你驚呢啲。好啦好啦，我開慢啲啦唉，驚你陣間嘔落我道，哈哈！」<br />\n阿軒又再次偷揶我說。<br />\n<br />\n在路途上也看到幾隻零零散散的喪屍在遊走，看來這一區依舊是安全的。<br />\n<br />\n過了幾分鐘，我們來到了將軍澳分區警署，我們小心翼翼的走進去，因為我們也不知道到底周圍有沒有其他人，畢竟我們也受過太多的埋伏，無論到哪也要提高警覺。<br />\n<br />\n我們首先步入槍聲庫，看看有沒有剩底的武器，好使我們較輕鬆應付喪屍。<br />\n<br />\n「阿希，呢邊有三把左輪，有幾十粒子彈，一人一把袋住先，另外個把我放入背囊。」<br />\n「嗯！呢邊都有多一支警棍同埋警盾，你拎住。」<br />\n<br />\n執拾完裝備後，我們開始找尋物資。<br />\n<br />\n我們上回跑車，駛到新都城的停車場，便向商場進發。<br />\n<br />\n沿途看到的商舖亦是空空如也，我想乾糧應該已被拿光了，但也是想碰碰運氣，於是我們便行到去惠康。<br />\n<br />\n「我們直接去倉吧。」<br />\n「嗯。」<br />\n因為我知道架上的食糧一定已經都被拿走，而在我們行進去的時候也是空空如也，所以我的推測也是正確，反應惠康倉還有一絲希望。<br />\n<br />\n「有個鎖喎！！」<br />\n「砰！」<br />\n我直接用槍把鎖頭射爆。<br />\n<br />\n「哇，嚇死人咩大佬。」<br />\n「快阿嘛，唔通你想玩解鎖遊戲？」<br />\n<br />\n的確在倉中還有很多物資未被拿走，<br />\n我們只是拿了大約能用7天的乾糧，裝滿了背包後，便準備離開。<br />\n<br />\n67完"},{"pid":"17731701c2c86999ac52d343fb36d424e253627f","tid":158213,"uid":31552,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-19T01:46:27.000Z","msg":"見今日都多人拜山 所以晨早流流出左先<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"741a459996b85e04e2fddbdb52ec552e306e501f","tid":158213,"uid":73000,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-19T02:18:34.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"d2cea6ae08bf9eac8651944520445811c6ca920b","tid":158213,"uid":61105,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-19T03:24:44.000Z","msg":"新都城咁旺都無屍<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/surprise.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"575ab74f17761a90fb2f6cbbb81e67a8d8c96104","tid":158213,"uid":15237,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-19T03:44:12.000Z","msg":"D 對話睇到我打撚哂冷震，同埋呀軒點會咁順攤跟你走，佢明明想自給自足<br />\n不過都加油啦"},{"pid":"b3fb51cf402af94583743b9072ad1d1d907e34c8","tid":158213,"uid":31552,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-19T04:06:00.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>新都城咁旺都無屍<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/surprise.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n準備黎料<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9701a1fd4b831e9f165a66feae4991a7a5ebe9b7","tid":158213,"uid":31552,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-19T04:07:22.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>D 對話睇到我打撚哂冷震，同埋呀軒點會咁順攤跟你走，佢明明想自給自足<br />\n不過都加油啦</blockquote><br />\n巴打唔好意思，會改善下。<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9179438b79f054e417790361c3e14fa849c371e7","tid":158213,"uid":61709,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-19T05:08:46.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>打鬥可以試下寫多啲，加啲唔同種類既招式，直拳，左勾拳，則踢，打左腰打雞心，會細緻啲<br />\n<br />\n同埋可以試下加方向，比如同隊長合擊個陣 我從左方 佢右方咁</blockquote><br />\n好既 多謝巴打指點<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n屌<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 原來回錯post 不過2個都用得著<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6ec293c2ef2a55fe36be1b6c83e041a7882efa24","tid":158213,"uid":31552,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-19T05:09:31.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>打鬥可以試下寫多啲，加啲唔同種類既招式，直拳，左勾拳，則踢，打左腰打雞心，會細緻啲<br />\n<br />\n同埋可以試下加方向，比如同隊長合擊個陣 我從左方 佢右方咁</blockquote><br />\n好既 多謝巴打指點<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n屌<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 原來回錯p